cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use EpiRec, please cite it as below."
title: "EpiRec: Episodic Recall — A Benchmark for Emotional Resurfacing and Factual Lookup in Memory-Augmented Agents"
version: "1.0"
date-released: 2026-07-13
repository-code: "https://github.com/sukoji/epirec"
license: CC-BY-4.0
type: dataset
authors:
  - family-names: Jin
    given-names: Seokho
abstract: >
  A synthetic, pre-registered, mechanically-validated benchmark for episodic-memory
  retrieval in journaling agents: 12 personas, 168 timestamped first-person episodes
  with authored emotional-intensity and valence labels, and 504 probes split into
  factual, reflective-explicit, and reflective-implicit types. Generated with
   an LLM-assisted, author-supervised synthetic corpus.
